It was reported that Kaul left a high-profile and lucrative job at Google India to join the reality TV show. Many prominent media outlets in India reported her story when she was declared a contestant for the show.

Kaul’s role on Bigg Boss 10 was initially praised by many in India and abroad. However, as the show progressed she became more controversial and online hangtags calling for her elimination surfaced on the internet."
            android:textColor="#181515"
            android:textSize="16dp" />

    </ScrollView>

    <Button
        android:id="@+id/verifyReg"
        style="@style/Widget.AppCompat.Button.Borderless.Colored"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="39dp"

        android:layout_alignParentBottom="true"
        android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
        android:background="@drawable/button_ui_bg"
        android:backgroundTint="@color/VerifyButton"
        android:text="Verify Resitration"

        android:textColor="@color/cardview_light_background"
        app:layout_constraintBottom_toBottomOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintStart_toStartOf="parent" />



</RelativeLayout>
